rlm-sandbox-bq-open

Browse BigQuery tables in a sandbox project via fzf and open the
selected table in the GCP console. The project and dataset list are
configured via environment variables (set in ~/.zshrc.thismachine).

The table list is cached in ~/.cache/sandbox-bq-open/items.txt.
Select "--- REFRESH CACHE ---" in the picker to re-fetch. The
selection history is kept in ~/.cache/sandbox-bq-open/history.txt
and survives cache refreshes.

Press Ctrl-P to cycle the preview pane height (40% → 70% → hidden).

ENVIRONMENT
  SANDBOX_BQ_PROJECT   GCP project ID to search (required).
  SANDBOX_BQ_DATASETS  Colon-separated list of dataset names to
                       include (required). Example:
                       ecerulm:ecerulm_dw:ecerulm_prep

REQUIRES
  bq, fzf, jq
